data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. MOTIVATED SELLERS, BRING YOUR OFFER! Beautifully updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in Central Tampa. New Windows just installed!  Home is move-in-ready and boasts a 2019 Roof, 2020 H2O Heater, Updated Kitchen and floors throughout and newer appliances including washer and dryer. The home itself is wonderful and when you consider the fully fenced backyard, carport, not to mention the 273 sq/ft under roof attached workshop, storage or she-shed you will have plenty of space to live near everything and keep a little something for yourself. Inside the home you will find updates galore! Years updated include: kitchen and bathrooms (2018), Floors (2022), Exterior Paint (2023) and windows (Aug 2023). Finding indoor laundry in a home this age is not easy, but this one has it. Ceiling fans in all rooms, updated bathrooms, pantry, 5.5 inch baseboards, you will be wowed! Outside the home a large oak tree stands guard on the front lawn, the backyard has a paver pergola (rain protected), a 10 by 10 garden shed and is perfect for your furry friend on day 1.  Walkable to both Foster Elementary School as well as Sligh Middle Magnet School. City bus stop 10 steps away, close to airport, hospitals, stadium. Seminole Heights East area of Tampa.
